    base:desc "The trajectory‑generator service produces optimal joint trajectories; the control application subscribes to these trajectories and translates them into motor step pulses sent to the motor drivers via the Python interface; the continuous‑validation service publishes alerts to the Grafana dashboard when measurement‑simulation divergence exceeds a predefined threshold; the operator can manually issue override commands through the GUI that are routed back to the control application."
]

